{
  "id": "69eb648a3fcbba661e58c3be",
  "title": "窒素飢餓",
  "created": 1777034405,
  "updated": 1777037391,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69eb648a3fcbba661e58c3be",
      "text": "窒素飢餓",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777034405,
      "updated": 1777034405
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb64a5000000000034f558",
      "text": "炭素率（C/N比）が高い有機物を土壌に大量に混ぜる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777034405,
      "updated": 1777034486
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb651b000000000034f55d",
      "text": "\t未熟な堆肥、未分解の有機物、稲藁、籾殻、バーク堆肥（樹皮を発酵させた堆肥）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777034523,
      "updated": 1777034591
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb64f6000000000034f55a",
      "text": "微生物がそれを分解するために土中の窒素を一時的に消費する",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777034486,
      "updated": 1777034488
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb64f8000000000034f55b",
      "text": "作物が吸収する窒素が不足する",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777034488,
      "updated": 1777034501
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb6505000000000034f55c",
      "text": "生育不良になる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777034501,
      "updated": 1777034505
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb6f42000000000054dfb7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "67bf02ec874ae1ce04e71b08",
      "created": 1777037122,
      "updated": 1777037290
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb6ff00000000000eeeb45",
      "text": "C/N比が高くても[リグニン]分解期まで熟成していれば、窒素飢餓は起こりにくいという考え方もある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1777037296,
      "updated": 1777037391
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb6f960000000000eeeb44",
